'''下東區'''<ref>{{cite web |last=Chozick |first=Amy |title=My Lower East Side |trans-title=狂野下東區，難逃士紳化難題？ |url=https://cn.nytimes.com/real-estate/20140822/t22lowereast/dual/ |website=[[紐約時報中文網|紐約時報中文網]] |date={{dts|2014|8|22}} |access-date={{dts|2019|9|1}} |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104014529/https://cn.nytimes.com/real-estate/20140822/t22lowereast/dual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Lower East Side}}，簡稱{{lang|en|LES}}），另譯'''下東城'''，是[[美國|美國]][[紐約市|紐約市]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]東南部的一片街區，其大致範圍從東到西涵蓋[[埃塞克斯街_(紐約)|埃塞克斯街]]、[[艾倫街_(曼哈頓)|艾倫街]]和[[埃爾德里奇街_(曼哈頓)|埃爾德里奇街]]，由南至北包括[[東百老匯大街|東百老匯大街]]、[[運河街_(曼哈頓)|運河街]]、[[格蘭街|格蘭街]]和東[[豪斯頓街|豪斯頓街]]。街區南側為[[華埠_(曼哈頓)|曼哈頓華埠]]，西側為{{link-en|諾麗塔|NoLIta}}，北側為[[東村_(紐約市)|東村]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Virshup |first=Amy |url=https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/fodors/top/features/travel/destinations/unitedstates/newyork/newyorkcity/fdrs_feat_111_13.html |title=New York Nabes |work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date= |access-date={{dts|2007|1|13}} |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027064824/https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/fodors/top/features/travel/destinations/unitedstates/newyork/newyorkcity/fdrs_feat_111_13.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=McEvers |first=Kelly |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/nyclife/0510,mcevers,61581,15.html |title=Close-Up on the Lower East Side |work={{link-en|The Village Voice}} |date={{dts|2005|3|2}} |access-date={{dts|2007|1|13}} |language=en-US |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061023102800/http://www1.villagevoice.com/nyclife/0510%2Cmcevers%2C61581%2C15.html |archive-date=2006-10-23 }}</ref>

下東區原本是一片移民、[[工人階級|工人階級]]街區，但於2005年前後經歷快速[[仕紳化|仕紳化]]，以至於{{link-en|國家歷史保護信託基金會 (美國)|National Trust for Historic Preservation|美國國家歷史保護信託基金會}}於2008年將這片街區列入{{link-en|美國最瀕危地點|America's Most Endangered Places}}名錄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap_travel/20080521/ap_tr_ge/travel_yesterday_s_places_endangered_places |title=Threats to history seen in budget cuts, bulldozers – Yahoo! News |website=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] |date= |access-date={{dts|2010|3|16}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013225755/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap_travel/20080521/ap_tr_ge/travel_yesterday_s_places_endangered_places |archive-date=2008-10-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。現在街區内不僅有高檔精品店，還有衆多沿克林頓街（{{lang|en|Clinton Street}}）分佈的高檔時尚餐飲場所。

